WEBVTT

00:00.660 --> 00:02.870
Carroll was convicted in 2004

00:02.880 --> 00:05.280
for the murders of 14 young women.

00:05.315 --> 00:06.365
Has Roderick told you

00:06.400 --> 00:07.485
what I'd like you
to do for me?

00:07.520 --> 00:09.720
He said you wanted me
to follow Ryan Hardy.

00:09.755 --> 00:11.790
- Molly. 
- Hey, neighbor.

00:12.290 --> 00:13.140
You don't want to do that, Claire.

00:13.175 --> 00:14.222
Take me to my son.

00:14.257 --> 00:15.270
What's next, Joe?

00:15.280 --> 00:16.515
Enjoying my family.

00:16.550 --> 00:18.555
Now that you have
your family back,

00:18.590 --> 00:20.270
can I tell the others
we're ready to start?

00:20.305 --> 00:20.925
Not just yet.

00:20.960 --> 00:22.100
I got a delivery.
Can I go?

00:22.135 --> 00:23.205
Make it quick.

00:23.240 --> 00:24.180
What is this place?

00:24.215 --> 00:25.182
A military armory.

00:25.217 --> 00:26.115
Training grounds.

00:26.150 --> 00:27.155
- For what?
- Killing.

00:27.190 --> 00:28.625
My men are securing
the building now.

00:28.660 --> 00:30.260
It's like they're running
some kind of boot camp.

00:30.295 --> 00:32.159
I want every inch
of this place processed.

00:32.195 --> 00:34.130
The FBI discovered the camp.

00:34.165 --> 00:35.160
Vince led them there.

00:35.195 --> 00:36.390
It's impossible.

00:36.710 --> 00:38.990
You don't make decisions anymore,
Roderick.

00:39.025 --> 00:40.390
I am here now.

00:40.400 --> 00:42.370
Joe would like you to join him
for dinner tonight.

00:44.200 --> 00:46.010
Want to see your son?
Make an effort.

00:46.045 --> 00:47.450
Please let me see Joey.

00:47.485 --> 00:48.275
Good try, Claire.

00:48.310 --> 00:50.400
This is going to continue to be a charade

00:50.435 --> 00:51.512
until I see my son!

00:51.547 --> 00:52.555
Bring me my son!

00:52.590 --> 00:54.970
I really do believe that
you will love me again.

00:55.005 --> 00:56.190
Mom!

00:56.460 --> 00:59.380
Oh, my god, Joey. Oh, baby. Ohh.

